## 7. Register IDbContextFactory

In Program.cs, change:
```
builder.Services.AddDbContext<ApplicationDbContext>(...)
```
to:
```
builder.Services.AddDbContextFactory<ApplicationDbContext>(...)
```

This is needed because interactive server components should use IDbContextFactory rather than directly injecting DbContext (which would be scoped to the circuit lifetime).

